data.title: In the Old Bank
data.text: From the exterior one would  never  know that there's  a Starbucks inside, as well as a bank. Located in the Orange traffic circle Chapman  and Glassel.  Glassel has many antique store and many restaurants. Now back to  the bank building. It has lots of architectural details such as a painted vaulted ceiling and plaster work. Comfortable chairs and tables to sit and enjoy. Did I mention  the Wells Fargo Bank? It's  tucked into the  back corner.

data.title: Great environment and plenty of space
data.text: This place should be a required visit just to look at, but when you think that you can meet here with friends or work meetings or just to study, because it has a large lobby, you can't loose.  Lots of tables space and elbow room to have that conversation that you dont want the whole world to hear.  Love the staff too!

data.title: Starbucks and some bank cash!
data.text: I've lived in Orange most of my life and this is still the closest 2 starbucks I've ever seen.  I could throw a rock from one starbucks to the next seriously about 60 yards away from the other and they both are always packed!  Crazy but cool.  I like to come to this one in the bank when I grab some cash.  It's really convenient.

data.title: Hot coffee
data.text: This location, even though right across the plaza from other star bucks, has HOT coffee. They make half caf a tad different than the other...making sure it was hot. Perfect!

data.title: Starbucks on the Orange Circle - Both Great!
data.text: There are two Starbucks in this corner and this applies to both - both are great Starbucks with different personalities if that makes any sense.  One is inside a Wells Fargo building (also open during non banking hours), which a significant size seating area and high ceilings.  The address listed here is for that one.  Both have great staffs and do their Starbucks drinks very well.  This is not be confused with the Starbucks by Best Buy farther up the street.  Total opposite to these two.  Come here if you want a great and relaxing experience.  But they do provide fast service!  You won't be disappointed!

data.title: it's a Starbucks
data.text: As expected, good service and great coffee drinks, just what you expect at a Starbucks.  Friendly service

data.title: it's just yummy
data.text: what can I say...it's fabulous! It's easy! Love the sugar free blended drinks. too bad not all of them are equal!

data.title: 立派
data.text: オレンジ市のダウンタウンにあるスターバックスで、昔の建物をそのまま改装して使っているおしゃれなスターバックスでした。周りはアンティークショップが多く、買い物の途中に休憩できるいいスポットです。
